Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不能常常回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子嘛\N总是会有很多东西要买
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  给你\N（洋芋片）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是干地瓜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给七宝的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  它还会自己转耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不胜感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想特别来和她会合的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得有机会回到故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是修理飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还有很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也许不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有个老爱摸屁股的色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该不需要担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第59话 美少女姐妹花拜师学艺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然无法\N像父亲一样技术那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言  算是很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲  还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于都回到故乡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直让你们这么孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能胜任驱魔师的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像很适合继承家业的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止接受的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是为了让你继承衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望你能坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您那时是想要说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你原谅芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经三天没吃没喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃呢  芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呢  你们要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一碗!\N再来一碗!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是姐姐芹菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠着传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找寻驱魔师隐密的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道我是驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会袭击我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想试试你的身手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是了得呢  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收我们为徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收你们?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们身手很不错喔  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父  请您一定要收我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通融一下嘛  师父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您  师父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是师父!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有急事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非您收我们当徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教导我们驱魔的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我们回不了故乡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们似乎有什么隐情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的村子是靠着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山坡上开垦而维持生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了稍微扩大田地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而开垦镇守之森的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却从此让妖怪们横行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还不只一两只而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有好几个村民牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能逃到其他地方的人还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是家里有老人\N与小孩的人却没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都过着不安的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇守之森有布下结界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得到有个驱魔师村的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔师村已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我去如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子里没有能支付给\N珊瑚姐姐的礼物或钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就不打算雇用驱魔师的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且村子很远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算赶走妖怪一两次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们还是会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其那样不如训练我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会为了大家而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一朝一夕能学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果只是赶走小妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许可以教你们一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是晚个一两天出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家应该会等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先给你们驱魔的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这附近试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要光看  快点扇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混合妖怪讨厌的药草\N与矿物的粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做就能驱魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护你们村子的话很够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些烟确实很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真的可以驱魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐  不  师父!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有更华丽的招式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只学个一招半式反而更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再教你们\N怎么制作这些粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚还没有回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  有件事想请教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人会因为被摸臀部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就背叛了彼此的信赖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相保持应有的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是一种信赖不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚没回来果然都是你害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然嘴巴说一定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却一点都冷静不下来呢  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐  看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入的技术我可是不输人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  父亲说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔师武器的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪们的牙齿  骨头与皮革
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们才能对付强悍的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说只要有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也能够…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…芹菜姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是一般的小女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种身手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是个忍者村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从城里接到了一个\N不熟悉的驱魔任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以忍术好不容易打倒妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到那些妖怪的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了报仇而袭击村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会用忍术的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎都成了妖怪的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜  铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只剩你们  也要坚强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸这么说完之后就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坚强…要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让村子再度恢复往日的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲一定是想这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们连尚未去除妖气\N的武器都带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发妖气的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会招来大批妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  姐姐老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪爸爸会期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由妹妹我来继承衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要持续修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定也能成为像父亲所说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强悍的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个  快坐上云母的背
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到村子里去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西快丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大群妖怪正朝着\N散发妖气的武器过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的!快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好打倒妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,争取逃走的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是让父亲见识\N我们的力量的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们毕竟是忍者村的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有能够除掉妖怪的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜  铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只剩你们  也要坚强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止接受的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是为了让你继承衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望你能坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们父亲所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是为了让你们这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有父亲不希望\N女儿们过的幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是希望你们继承衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是希望你们坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  坐上云母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧紧的跟在我后面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜  铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只剩你们  也要坚强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并得到幸福  才是他期盼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么!芹菜姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚姐姐说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙也费这么大劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一点都不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个要坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为弥勒这家伙一直在担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了之后果然不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  幸好赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的这么担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的预感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  因为你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在我眼前浮现\N挥之不去的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊  弥勒一族
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想变成那种大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:31.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:38.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:46.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:54.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.17,0:25:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.00,0:25:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那家伙竟然带着以前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和桔梗对决过的邪恶巫女来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.74,0:25:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  完全都看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.24,0:25:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟不上进度了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.44,0:25:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙利用四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.98,0:25:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对你施放可怕的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.21,0:25:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都叫我和犬夜叉分手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.01,0:25:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.18,0:25:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.75,0:25:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人都说你是\N暴力劈腿吃醋男
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.85,0:25:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?那是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.95,0:25:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.26,0:25:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑巫女 五十年的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.26,0:25:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.49,0:25:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思啦?
